本論文永久網址:      Twitter研究生:周宗德研究生(外文):Tsung-Te CHOU論文名稱:苗慄縣文化創意產業與觀光節慶活動發展之探討指導教授:黃國敏學位類別:碩士校院名稱:中華大學系所名稱:經營管理研究所學門:商業及管理學門學類:企業管理學類論文出版年:2007畢業學年度:95語文別:中文論文頁數:176中文關鍵詞:文化創意產業、文化產業、社區總體營造、節慶活動、SWOT外文關鍵詞:cultural creative industry、culture industry、community building、special events、SWOT相關次數:

被引用:42點閱:1957評分:下載:641書目收藏:31



隨著全球化與科技化兩股風潮，21世紀的經濟型態已經轉變為以創新為主的知識經濟型態，而「文化創意產業」也就在此時空背景下因應而生，期望將原有的「文化產業」加入創新的元素，以帶動地方經濟的發展。在苗慄縣無論是傳統文化產業如華陶窯、木雕、客家文化，抑或近年逐漸大放光彩的桐花祭活動，都面臨著轉型的關鍵期，必須註入創新元素以滿足不同消費者的需求，才不致使上述傳統產業遭到淘汰。地方政府舉辦各具地方特色的節慶活動，並以文化產業化以及產業文化化的包裝手法藉以廣招外地遊客前來消費。近年來，國內的觀光節慶蓬勃發展，而苗慄縣境內也舉辦不少節慶活動，如「三義國際木雕藝術節」、「國際假面藝術節」、「苗慄龍國際文化節」，以及象徵客家文化的「桐花祭」…等。本研究之目的在於：1、探討目前國內、外文化創意產業發展的概況與經驗；2、以「三義丫箱寶」與「苑裡華陶窯」為個案探討苗慄縣文化創意產業的發展及其所遭遇之困境；3、以SWOT分析苗栗縣發展文化創意產業的內部優勢與劣勢及外部的機會與威脅；4、苗慄縣所推出的節慶活動的構想、內容及其與在地產業的關聯性；5、以研究發現為基礎，針對苗慄縣未來在發展文化創意產業及舉辦節慶活動提出建議。研究發現如下：1、文化創意產業的出路－與節慶活動連結。若節慶與在地產業連結好，對於節慶將有加分效果；2、工廠轉型創意產業：一丫箱寶。若能結合政府政策，加上自身優勢，不僅能永續經營，更可增進傳統產業發展；3、堅持傳統台灣文化：華陶窯。需要更多的資金和人才，以及整體環境行銷配合，必須作更長期的規劃。

Following the trend of both globalization and technology, the economic style for 21 century has already transformed into the knowledge-based economy style mainly according to innovation, and thus the “culture creative industry” emerged under such background, in expectation to add the innovation factor into original “culture industry” to stimulate local economic development. No matter the traditional cultural industry, such as Hwataoyao, wood carving, the Hakka culture, or the blooming flower season activity arose in the resent years, all are facing a critical period of transformation; if they can't add creative element to satisfy the needs of different consumers, the above-mentioned traditional industry would be possible to be eliminated.The local government design elaborate of festivals to attract visitors. In recent years, there are many tourist festivals appearing in Taiwan, and Miao-Li County had also held some special events, such as Sanyi Wood carving Festival, International Mask Festival, Miao-Li Fireddragon International Cultural Festival and the symbol of Hakka Culture－Tung Blossom Festival, etc.The purposes of the study are:1. Investigation of the general developing situation and experiences of the culture creative industry among Taiwan and foreign countries; 2. Investigation of the development and the encountering problems of the culture creative industry in Miao-Li County－The case study of Duckdiy in Sanyi and Hwatao kiln in Yuanli; 3. The SWOT Analysis of the culture creative industry’s internal strengths and weakness, and external opportunities and threats in Miao-Li County; 4. Investigation of the ideas and contents of the special events pushed on by  Miao-Li County, and its relationship with local industry; 5. According to the research findings, provides the suggestions focusing on developing the culture creative industry and holding the special events in Miao-Li County in the future.The research findings show as following: 1. The path of the culture creative industry－connect with special events. If special events can connect with local industry well, it will benefit to special events; 2. The factory turns into the culture creative industry: Duckdiy. If it can combine with government’s policy, not only can attain sustainable management, but also can increase the development of traditional industry; 3. Insisting on the traditional Taiwan Culture: Hwatao kiln. It needs more cash and staff , also the match of entire environment marketing; which must take a  long-period planning.

